---
By: Baird Spalding
Locus:
  Page: 182
  Verse: 17
Tags:
  - Giving
---
To receive more, we must give out what we receive. ...For it is by giving
that we set in operation the unfailing law of measure for measure. With no
thought of receiving, it is impossible to avoid receiving, for the
abundance you have given is returned to you in fulfillment of the law.
